      "variants": [
        "\"Very well, let's proceed with the trial you're so set on.\"",
        "\"So be it. We'll have your trial, then.\"",
        "\"Alright. Let's get on with this trial you crave.\"",
        "\"If you insist on a trial, then let's have it.\""
